Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:49.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:54.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:59.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:04.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:09.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:30.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:40.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:47.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:53.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:03:00.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:04.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.17,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:49.09,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:54.22,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光暈  浮現於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:59.43,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,未見未知的陽光  會將誰照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:04.19,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,我親愛的伙伴  就算沉浸於悲傷也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:09.15,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.44,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  來伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.82,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿過這片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.03,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  衝擊全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.66,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.33,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,緊盯著世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:30.17,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,當小小胸膛填滿了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:40.10,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,琥珀之夢  朝著約定的地點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:47.48,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,對你的關心關愛  比這天空更寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:53.61,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,無限擴張  永無止境
Comment: 0,0:02:53.61,0:03:00.54,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:04.41,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:21.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I want to go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:27.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}住み慣れたこの街を出てゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:31.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}新しい世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:35.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}まだ見ぬ色を　探しに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:36.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I can not do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:42.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}素直になれないこともあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}あの虹の向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}行ってみたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:56.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}頭に浮かんだイメージを抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:02.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I will never ever give up halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:10.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}どこまでも　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:17.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I wanna make my life shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:28.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}輝くよ　あの虹の向こうまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:21.82,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想要出發
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:27.95,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}離開這熟悉的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:31.12,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}去探索新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:35.04,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}尋找從未見過的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:36.50,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:42.47,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}有時也會不夠坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.59,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}那彩虹的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.43,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想試著去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:56.06,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}記住浮現在頭腦中的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:02.90,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我永遠不會半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:10.49,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不論到哪裡  不論走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:17.50,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想讓自己的生命更閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:28.43,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}釋放光芒吧  直到那彩虹的彼端
